parameters: \nc<>Even if I go this far, will it not reach you...?

\nc<>Now, it's time for you to deliver the finishing blow to
me.

\nc<>If you keep hesitating, I will attack you from behind again
with the power of darkness.

\nc<>(...I will admit it. I cannot restore this person to their
original state.) (My words hold no weight for this person.)

\nc<>(At least, so that this person doesn't make any more
mistakes...)

\nc<>Why? Because this is my line! Why do you just give up and
try to disappear on your own as if it's natural?

\nc<>(If you look closely, there are traces of slime here and
there.) (They really chased after me all the way here
alone.)
\nc<>I don't think what the leader was doing was good.

\nc<>But, even if it's something the leader dreamed of, I thought
it couldn't be helped, so I refused Levantia-san's proposal.
\nc<>What is it? Something that you wouldn't normally do!

\nc<>If it's the result of such a compromise, wouldn't it have
been better not to do something like this from the
beginning!?

\nc<>Even though I, who used to be a man of just empty words,
have obtained the power to fulfill even half of my dreams--

\nc<>The place that the leader created was a paradise for me, at
least!

\nc<>If what I obtained by destroying that, um, if the leader
says it's only half, then I, how should I put it...

\nc<>(Yukiko-chan... I couldn't put my thoughts into words and
ended up crying.)

\nc<>(Well, it seems like it was properly conveyed to the person
who should have understood it.)
\nc<>Well, who knows? I don't really have any thoughts on it.

\nc<>But what is certain is that you were able to fulfill your
dreams, even if only a little.
\nc<>Is that so? Wasn't what I was doing not meaningless...?
\nc<>D-Did they really turn back into a human!?
\nc<>I see, if I can reject that power, I can become like this.

\nc<>Huh? Ah, don't worry. Magical girls are the righteous
heroes who protect people from villains.
\nc<>I will protect both of you properly.
\nc<>Well, I think they should receive punishment, but meow.
\nc<>Don't ruin the good atmosphere we had.
\nc<>I obtained the memory N6: Defeating Mr. Hypnosis.

\nc<>The number of good listeners increased by 7,000, and the
number of bad listeners increased by 3,000.
